          br      
          h4 Getting Data
          br
          .panel.panel-default
            .panel-body
              | Request are made over HTTPS using both GET.          
          br
          h5
            b Questionnaire Conducting and Conducted Id's
          pre(style='padding: 0px 30px;') 
            code
              .panel.panel-default
                .panel-body
                  i https://api.themindspot.com/r/*AccessKey*
              p
