              br
          h5 Example
          .panel.panel-default(style='padding: 0px 30px;') 
            .panel-body
              i GET https://api.themindspot.com/r/dc06376e-d658-4d27-bff7-ae04733fe412/responses/5521559bdb41e8b51b21e96e
